! Address-First Search Protocol

A retrieval route that starts with Bloom/regime/index/spiral traversal before
edge expansion and hash verification.

!! Why It Matters

It turns [[Internal Semantic Search]] into an executable order of operations:
address candidates first, graph expansion second, integrity receipts always.

